Introducing the Kupocard Mini 2!

Until Wed., Mar. 27, 07:59 UTC

Introducing the limited-time Kupocard Mini 2!

The Kupocard Mini 2 will give you 1,050 Initial Gems and seven days of 350 Daily Gems － that's a total of 3,500 Gems!

If you purchase the Kupocard Mini 2 four times (maximum) during the campaign, you can receive a grand total of 14,000 Gems!

It will be here until Wed., Mar. 27, at 07:59 UTC, so don't miss out!

About the Kupocard Mini 2

Kupocard Mini 2

  • Initial Gems: 1,050
  • Daily Gems: 350 (for 7 days)
  • Total Gems: 3,500

Upon purchase, you will receive the Initial Gems immediately, and the Daily Gems will be sent to your Gift Box alongside your Daily Bonus from your next login, for a total of 7 logins.

After receiving the seventh Daily Gems reward, you can purchase another Kupocard Mini 2 as long as it is within the campaign period. This means you can get up to four during this period!

You can purchase the Kupocard Mini alongside the Kupocard Mini 2.

* Logins do not need to be consecutive for you to receive all 7 login bonuses.
* Login bonuses reset at 08:00 UTC.
* You can confirm how many logins remain on your Kupocard(s) by tapping on the "Kupocards" button on the Gifts screen.
